Comment: 1,0:00:44.98,0:00:45.48,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.48,0:00:47.61,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,開端便是一切都順序錯亂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.61,0:00:50.49,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,一成不變的生活地覆天翻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.49,0:00:53.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,很久很久很久以前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.37,0:00:56.24,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,人還知吃吃喝喝舞中作樂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.24,0:00:58.91,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,今辛酸痛苦無止境  社會壓力超負荷
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.75,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早間新聞將這常態播放著
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.75,0:01:03.46,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,逼著我睜開雙眼  漱口洗臉
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早餐一個漢堡打發  能不能來點奇蹟使天地異變
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.55,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做什麼夢呢我傻嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.55,0:01:08.92,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.01,0:01:10.59,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,I wanna!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.93,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing, dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.93,0:01:13.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Rolling, rolling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.43,0:01:15.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Only one, my life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.68,0:01:18.97,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,不久後人生即將畫上句號
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,僅有空虛又怎夠將我填飽？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.06,0:01:23.19,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.19,0:01:24.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Morning morning
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.77,0:01:30.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,立足原點  保持新鮮
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.15,0:01:33.32,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做我所願
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.12,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Every night, every time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.12,0:01:43.04,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,活至盡興  玩到疲倦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.63,0:01:47.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
